column2: All other cells (excluding year+winners_rank+winners_show) are JSON strings that must not contain commas NOR quotes NOR newlines.
The year cells must be JSON numbers.  The winners_rank cells must be a JSON number or JSON null.  The winners_show cells must be JSON booleans.
Empty cells are filled in with red and need to be filled in and are TBD.
Any cell containing null is a JSON null value. Any cell containing true or false is a JSON boolean value.
